    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "gRPC code does **not** manage certificates. It is up to caller to monitor the life-cycle of certificate (and restart gRPC binary if needed when certificate expires).\r\ngRPC security API does provide credential reloading capability\r\nhttps://github.com/grpc/grpc/blob/master/include/grpc/grpc_security.h#L406\r\nWith credential reloading, it is possible to reload a new certificate without re-starting your binary."
  },
